Available Tools: create_deal | update_deal_stage | get_deal | list_deals_by_stage | close_deal
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "deal_id": "string", "contact_id": "string", "stage": "string", "value": number }
Response Schema: { "deal_id": "string", "name": "string", "stage": "string", "value": number, "probability": number }
---
Question: Initiate a new prospect deal for Globex Corporation with contact ID C-7701 valued at 23000.
Call: { "func_call": "create_deal", "deal_id": "D-5001", "contact_id": "C-7701", "stage": "prospect", "value": 23000 }
Response: { "deal_id": "D-5001", "name": "Globex Logistics Setup", "stage": "prospect", "value": 23000, "probability": 10 }

Question: Transition deal D-6002 to the qualified stage for contact C-8802, adjusting the value to 56000.
